What you need to know:

The Bill sponsored by nominated MCA Elizabeth Wacheke Gichuki proposes the tough measure to address management of solid waste, effluent and other hazardous waste that ends up in Lake Nakuru National Park.The proposed regulation further says that individuals or firms that dump waste on land or any other place not designated for this shall be guilty of an offence and upon conviction, will pay a fine of not less than Sh200,000.